title: Carnival Cravings with Anthony Anderson S01E01.PDTV.x264-JIVE.mp
description:
Anthony Anderson is diving headfirst into summer with the ultimate vacation road trip, exploring the country's best carnivals. Whether they're ooey, gooey, crispy or crunchy, Anthony lets America's favorite carnival indulgences lead the way on a coast-to-coast adventure. Nothing says summertime fun like a carnival!




Carnival Cravings with Anthony Anderson - Season 1, Episode 1


Sweet Carolina Cravings

Anthony Anderson heads to the Got to Be NC Festival in Raleigh, N.C. for some Southern-fried carnival goodness. He tickles his taste buds with everything from redneck egg rolls to the most intense bacon-wrapped deep-fried dessert this side of the Mississippi. After his belly has settled, he tries his hand at the lumberjack competition and bets the farm at the pig races.



Original Air Date: 12-Aug-2015
